        <note>See <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/QT6D2TPP"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Kropp1989Haylu"/><title level="m">Die äthiopischen Königschroniken in der Sammlung des Däǧǧazmač Ḫaylu: Entstehung und handschriftliche Überlieferung des Werks</title><title level="s">Heidelberger orientalische Studien</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Manfred</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Kropp</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Frankfurt a. M.</pubPlace><publisher>Lang</publisher><date>1989</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Heidelberger orientalische Studien</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">13</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">13</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">113-143</citedRange></bibl>. This originally
